column1: # Title: water demand (all sectors) by basin for water supply calibration period
# Source: queried from prior GCAM calibration period run
# Comments: This data is used solely for calibrating accessible water fractions using historical runoff and groundwater extraction rates. It is not used to set up water demand in GCAM.
# Comments: ... Actual GCAM Water demands are determined dynamically within the model for each sector (see sean.turner@pnnl.gov for details)
